data.description: Seller concessions available. Beautiful home with tons of natural light, large fenced backyard, and covered front porch.  Plenty of room for entertaining, gardening, and so much more! The large primary suite has a vaulted ceiling, a full bathroom with double sinks, and a walk-in closet. Nema 14-50 charging station installed for EV charging and/or RV use.  Room for an RV. New gas furnace just installed. High-speed 50mbps internet included.
